    {
        "content": "<p><code>ring</code> isn't expected to handle division; <code>field_simp</code> might help</p>",
        "id": 479215501,
        "sender_full_name": "Ruben Van de Velde",
        "timestamp": 1730102548
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Also, you are right about <code>0</code> being special-cased: <code>a / a</code> can be equal to <code>0</code>, when <code>a = 0</code>.</p>",
        "id": 479215654,
        "sender_full_name": "Damiano Testa",
        "timestamp": 1730102626
